An illustration of the sonar ant task failing with Debian Ant and java6. 

The debian bug is https://bugs.debian.org/cgi-bin/bugreport.cgi?bug=764376

As of 2014-11-17 the fix has arrived in Ubuntu. 

The problem was caused by the logger (logback) failing to find 
an XML parser to read its configuration. 

Sonar 4.4 installed and run with default settings 

The project now builds with 
Apache Ant(TM) version 1.9.4 compiled on April 29 2014 (current apache)
Apache Ant(TM) version 1.9.4 compiled on September 30 2014 (current testing)
Apache Ant(TM) version 1.9.4 compiled on October 7 2014 (current Ubuntu)


